reviewText: We had these movies on some old vhs tapes that my grandson started watching but the tapes finally gave out. He freaked out! This DVD from you guys is perfect, perfect, perfect thank you so much. It came fast too!
Our grandson loved it as much as his mother did at his age. Wonderful family movie! A movie for all ages!
I ordered this video for my grandson. He had the first movie and loved it. After seeing the previews for some of the other Land Before Time videos, he requested more. He loves watching these movies.
not as educational as PBS dinosaur train but my child loves it because they are more like stories. he watches it all the time
All of my kids have loved these movies. They're classic films perfect for little kids and up. Great lessons and great music. A must have in your movie vault.

Teenhood memories! I love these movies, they are the last of innocent movies , of course it does show how the circle of life works, survival of the fittest. My son loves the movies and are great for anyone to enjoy.
